content: One hundred, two hundred, three hundred, four hundred, five hundred, six hundred, seven hundred, eight hundred, nine hundred, one thousand.
translations: ita:Cento, duecento, trecento, quattrocento, cinquecento, seicento, settecento, ottocento, novecento, mille
